{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031205135417ccbeef022044f6","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"id":"2026031205135417ccbeef022044f6","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cdebfd06760b7d02cd331bbc03246","name":"Task","input":{"description":"PM: Specify+Plan+Tasks for F-008","prompt":"Read /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.codebuddy/agents/prizm-dev-team-pm.md. For feature F-008 (slug: 008-commit-workflow-integration), complete all three planning steps in this single session:\n\n1. Run prizmkit-specify → generate `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/spec.md` (concise, under 150 lines)\n2. Run prizmkit-plan → generate `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/plan.md` (architecture, components, interface design, data model, testing strategy — all in one file)\n3. Run prizmkit-tasks → generate `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/tasks.md` with `[ ]` checkboxes\n\nAll three files go under `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/`.\n\nFeature Description:\n打通 Telegram 侧\"规划→开发→测试→提交\"的闭环提交能力：在 pipeline 通过后可触发标准提交流程，回传 commit 结果摘要,并在前置条件不满足时阻止提交。该功能不涉及部署上线，只覆盖代码提交阶段。\n\nAcceptance Criteria:\n- 支持从 Telegram 触发标准提交动作并返回 commit hash 与摘要\n- 提交前会校验测试结果与 pipeline 状态，不满足条件则拒绝提交\n- 提交失败时返回明确失败原因与建议操作\n- 提交记录可在会话中追踪并与对应 feature/bugfix 关联\n\nDependencies (Already Completed):\n- F-005 - Pipeline Status and Log Streaming (completed)\n- F-006 - Safety and Permission Guard (completed)\n- F-007 - Test and Validation Suite (completed)\n\nTech Stack: Node.js + Express + Telegraf + JSON state files + Shell/Python dev-pipeline\nTesting: Jest (unit + integration)","subagent_type":"prizm-dev-team-pm","team_name":"prizm-dev-team"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":30749,"output_tokens":576,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_too