{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312051451d68dc39f668442e7","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"id":"20260312051451d68dc39f668442e7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Step 2: Run prizmkit.plan → plan.md"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdebfd06760b7d02cd331bbc03246","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:15:38.915Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312051451d68dc39f668442e7","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"id":"20260312051451d68dc39f668442e7","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cdec0a8c2d717df5a32d477cfff3a","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/plan.md","content":"# F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Technical Plan\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                        Telegram Bot                              │\n│  /commit, /commits commands                                      │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Command Handler Layer                               │\n│  src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js                             │\n│  src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js                            │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Security Layer (F-006)                              │\n│  PermissionGuard → ConfirmationManager → AuditLogService         │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Commit Service Layer                                │\n│  src/services/commit-service.js                                  │\n│  ├── validatePreConditions() → StatusAggregator                  │\n│  ├── executeCommit() → GitService                                │\n│  └── recordCommit() → SessionStore                               │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Infrastructure Layer                                │\n│  src/services/git-service.js (simple-git wrapper)                │\n│  src/services/status-aggregator.js (F-005)                       │\n│  src/services/session-store.js                                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Component Design\n\n### C-1: GitService (`src/services/git-service.js`)\n\n**Purpose:** 封装所有 git 操作，提供统一 API\n\n**Methods:**\n```javascript\ninterface GitService {\n  // 状态检查\n  getStatus(): Promise<GitStatus>\n  isClean(): Promise<boolean>\n  getChangedFiles(): Promise<string[]>\n  \n  // 提交操作\n  commit(message: string, options?: CommitOptions): Promise<CommitResult>\n  amendCommit(message: string): Promise<CommitResult>\n  getLastCommit(): Promise<CommitInfo>\n  \n  // 信息获取\n  getCommitLog(count?: number): Promise<CommitInfo[]>\n  getShortHash(hash: string): string\n}\n\ninterface GitStatus {\n  clean: boolean\n  staged: string[]\n  modified: string[]\n  untracked: string[]\n  conflicts: string[]\n  ahead: number\n  behind: number\n  currentBranch: string\n}\n\ninterface CommitResult {\n  success: boolean\n  hash?: string\n  shortHash?: string\n  message?: string\n  filesChanged?: number\n  error?: string\n  suggestion?: string\n}\n\ninterface CommitOptions {\n  amend?: boolean\n  allowEmpty?: boolean\n}\n```\n\n### C-2: CommitService (`src/services/commit-service.js`)\n\n**Purpose:** 提交业务逻辑编排，协调校验、执行、记录\n\n**Methods:**\n```javascript\ninterface CommitService {\n  // 主入口\n  commit(params: CommitParams): Promise<CommitResult>\n  \n  // 校验\n  validatePreConditions(options: ValidationOptions): Promise<ValidationResult>\n  \n  // 记录\n  recordCommit(sessionId: string, commitInfo: CommitInfo): Promise<void>\n  getSessionCommits(sessionId: string): Promise<CommitRecord[]>\n}\n\ninterface CommitParams {\n  sessionId: string\n  userId: string\n  message?: string\n  amend?: boolean\n  force?: boolean\n  featureId?: string\n  bugfixId?: string\n}\n\ninterface ValidationOptions {\n  skipPipelineCheck?: boolean\n  skipTestCheck?: boolean\n}\n\ninterface ValidationResult {\n  valid: boolean\n  errors: ValidationError[]\n  warnings: ValidationWarning[]\n}\n\ninterface ValidationError {\n  code: string\n  message: string\n  suggestion: string\n}\n\ninterface CommitRecord {\n  hash: string\n  shortHash: string\n  message: string\n  timestamp: number\n  author: string\n  featureId?: string\n  bugfixId?: string\n  filesChanged: number\n}\n```\n\n### C-3: Commit Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js`)\n\n**Purpose:** Telegram 命令处理入口\n\n**Flow:**\n1. 解析命令参数 (`--message`, `--amend`, `--force`)\n2. 权限检查 (`operator` for commit, `admin` for amend/force)\n3. 高风险操作确认流程 (amend/force)\n4. 调用 CommitService.commit()\n5. 格式化返回结果\n6. 记录审计日志\n\n### C-4: Commits Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js`)\n\n**Purpose:** 查看会话提交历史\n\n**Flow:**\n1. 获取当前会话 ID\n2. 调用 CommitService.getSessionCommits()\n3. 格式化历史列表返回\n\n---\n\n## Interface Design\n\n### I-1: Pre-Commit Validation API\n\n```javascript\n// src/services/commit-service.js\n\nconst VALIDATION_ERRORS = {\n  PIPELINE_RUNNING: {\n    code: 'PIPELINE_RUNNING',\n    message: 'Pipeline 正在运行中',\n    suggestion: '请等待 pipeline 完成或使用 /stop 停止'\n  },\n  TEST_FAILED: {\n    code: 'TEST_FAILED',\n    message: '测试未通过',\n    suggestion: '请检查测试结果或使用 --force 跳过（仅 admin）'\n  },\n  NOTHING_TO_COMMIT: {\n    code: 'NOTHING_TO_COMMIT',\n    message: '没有待提交的变更',\n    suggestion: '请先进行代码修改'\n  },\n  MERGE_CONFLICT: {\n    code: 'MERGE_CONFLICT',\n    message: '存在合并冲突',\n    suggestion: '请先解决以下冲突文件：{files}'\n  }\n};\n\nasync function validatePreConditions(options) {\n  const errors = [];\n  const warnings = [];\n  \n  // 1. Check pipeline status (via status-aggregator)\n  const pipelineStatus = await statusAggregator.aggregateStatus();\n  if (pipelineStatus.phase === 'running' && !options.skipPipelineCheck) {\n    errors.push(VALIDATION_ERRORS.PIPELINE_RUNNING);\n  }\n  \n  // 2. Check test status (from state file)\n  const testStatus = await getTestStatus();\n  if (testStatus.failed > 0 && !options.skipTestCheck) {\n    errors.push(VALIDATION_ERRORS.TEST_FAILED);\n  }\n  \n  // 3. Check git status\n  const gitStatus = await gitService.getStatus();\n  if (gitStatus.clean) {\n    errors.push(VALIDATION_ERRORS.NOTHING_TO_COMMIT);\n  }\n  if (gitStatus.conflicts.length > 0) {\n    errors.push({\n      ...VALIDATION_ERRORS.MERGE_CONFLICT,\n      files: gitStatus.conflicts\n    });\n  }\n  \n  return {\n    valid: errors.length === 0,\n    errors,\n    warnings,\n    gitStatus\n  };\n}\n```\n\n### I-2: Commit Execution API\n\n```javascript\n// src/services/git-service.js\n\nasync function commit(message, options = {}) {\n  try {\n    // Build commit message with footer\n    const fullMessage = buildCommitMessage(message, options);\n    \n    // Execute git commit\n    const result = await git.commit(fullMessage);\n    \n    if (!result.commit) {\n      return {\n        success: false,\n        error: '提交失败',\n        suggestion: '请检查 git 状态'\n      };\n    }\n    \n    return {\n      success: true,\n      hash: result.commit,\n      shortHash: result.commit.substring(0, 7),\n      message: fullMessage,\n      filesChanged: result.summary.changes\n    };\n  } catch (error) {\n    return {\n      success: false,\n      error: error.message,\n      suggestion: getSuggestion(error)\n    };\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### I-3: Session Commit Tracking\n\n```javascript\n// 扩展 src/services/session-store.js\n\n// Session state structure (JSON file)\n{\n  \"sessionId\": \"abc123\",\n  \"featureId\": \"F-008\",\n  \"createdAt\": 1710489600000,\n  \"commits\": [\n    {\n      \"hash\": \"a1b2c3d4e5f6...\",\n      \"shortHash\": \"a1b2c3d\",\n      \"message\": \"feat: add commit workflow\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1710489700000,\n      \"author\": \"user\",\n      \"filesChanged\": 5\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n// API\nasync function addCommitToSession(sessionId, commitInfo) {\n  const session = await loadSession(sessionId);\n  session.commits = session.commits || [];\n  session.commits.push({\n    ...commitInfo,\n    timestamp: Date.now()\n  });\n  await saveSession(session);\n}\n\nasync function getSessionCommits(sessionId) {\n  const session = await loadSession(sessionId);\n  return session.commits || [];\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Model\n\n### D-1: Session State (Extended)\n\n```javascript\n// File: data/sessions/{sessionId}.json\n{\n  \"sessionId\": \"string\",\n  \"featureId\": \"string | null\",\n  \"bugfixId\": \"string | null\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"number (timestamp)\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"number (timestamp)\",\n  \"commits\": [\n    {\n      \"hash\": \"string (full hash)\",\n      \"shortHash\": \"string (7 chars)\",\n      \"message\": \"string\",\n      \"timestamp\": \"number\",\n      \"author\": \"string\",\n      \"filesChanged\": \"number\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### D-2: Test Status (Existing)\n\n```javascript\n// File: dev-pipeline/state/test-status.json (由 F-007 创建)\n{\n  \"lastRun\": \"number (timestamp)\",\n  \"passed\": \"number\",\n  \"failed\": \"number\",\n  \"skipped\": \"number\",\n  \"duration\": \"number (ms)\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Command Permission Matrix\n\n| Command | Min Role | Confirmation | Notes |\n|---------|----------|--------------|-------|\n| `/commit` | operator | No | 标准提交 |\n| `/commit --amend` | admin | Yes | 修改最近提交 |\n| `/commit --force` | admin | Yes | 跳过校验 |\n| `/commits` | viewer | No | 查看历史 |\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Module | Test File | Coverage Target |\n|--------|-----------|-----------------|\n| GitService | tests/services/git-service.test.js | 90% |\n| CommitService | tests/services/commit-service.test.js | 90% |\n| commit handler | tests/bot/commands/handlers/commit.test.js | 85% |\n| commits handler | tests/bot/commands/handlers/commits.test.js | 85% |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Scenario | Test File | Priority |\n|----------|-----------|----------|\n| commit → success flow | tests/integration/commit-flow.test.js | High |\n| commit → validation failure | tests/integration/commit-validation.test.js | High |\n| commit → amend flow | tests/integration/commit-amend.test.js | Medium |\n| commit → force flow | tests/integration/commit-force.test.js | Medium |\n\n### Mock Strategy\n\n- GitService: 使用 mock git responses，不执行真实 git 命令\n- StatusAggregator: 复用 F-005 mock 策略\n- SessionStore: 使用临时目录\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\nsrc/\n├── services/\n│   ├── git-service.js          # NEW - git 操作封装\n│   ├── commit-service.js       # NEW - 提交业务逻辑\n│   └── session-store.js        # EXTEND - 添加 commit tracking\n├── bot/\n│   └── commands/\n│       └── handlers/\n│           ├── commit.js       # NEW - /commit 命令\n│           └── commits.js      # NEW - /commits 命令\ntests/\n├── services/\n│   ├── git-service.test.js     # NEW\n│   └── commit-service.test.js  # NEW\n├── bot/\n│   └── commands/\n│       └── handlers/\n│           ├── commit.test.js  # NEW\n│           └── commits.test.js # NEW\n└── integration/\n    ├── commit-flow.test.js     # NEW\n    └── commit-validation.test.js # NEW\n```\n\n---\n\n## User Story Mapping\n\n| User Story | Components | Key Files |\n|------------|------------|-----------|\n| US-1: Telegram Commit Trigger | C-3, C-2 | commit.js, commit-service.js |\n| US-2: Pre-Commit Validation | C-2 | commit-service.js |\n| US-3: Commit Result Feedback | C-1, C-3 | git-service.js, commit.js |\n| US-4: Session Commit Tracking | C-2, C-4 | commit-service.js, session-store.js, commits.js |\n| US-5: High-Risk Commit Protection | Security Layer | commit.js, permission-guard.js |\n\n---\n\n## Risk Mitigation\n\n| Risk | Mitigation Strategy |\n|------|---------------------|\n| Git 操作失败 | GitService 返回详细错误 + 建议操作 |\n| 工作目录脏状态 | 提交前 isClean() 检查 |\n| 测试状态文件缺失 | 容错处理，视为\"未运行测试\"警告 |\n| 会话文件损坏 | try-catch + 空数组回退 |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies Check\n\n| Dependency | Required By | Install Command |\n|------------|-------------|-----------------|\n| simple-git | GitService | `npm install simple-git` |\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n\n| ID | Date | Decision |\n|----|------|----------|\n| D1 | 2026-03-15 | 使用 simple-git 库封装 git 操作，避免 shell 注入风险 |\n| D2 | 2026-03-15 | Pre-commit 校验包含 pipeline 状态和测试状态双重检查 |\n| D3 | 2026-03-15 | 提交记录存储于会话状态文件，不新建独立存储 |\n| D4 | 2026-03-15 | 复用 F-006 确认机制处理 amend/force 高风险操作 |\n| D5 | 2026-03-15 | GitService 设计为可 mock，便于单元测试 |\n"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":30260,"output_tokens":3265,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdebfd06760b7d02cd331bbc03246","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:15:38.941Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
