{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031205153999fde7a4a9be4281","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"id":"2026031205153999fde7a4a9be4281","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cdec16280297e7063684cef515048","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/tasks.md","content":"# F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Task Breakdown\n\n## Phase 1: Setup (T-001 ~ T-009)\n\n- [ ] [T-001] [P] Install simple-git dependency — file: package.json\n- [ ] [T-002] [P] Create git-service.js module skeleton — file: src/services/git-service.js\n- [ ] [T-003] [P] Create commit-service.js module skeleton — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n- [ ] [T-004] [P] Create commit handler skeleton — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n- [ ] [P] Create commits handler skeleton — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js\n- [ ] [T-006] [P] Create test file skeletons — file: tests/services/git-service.test.js, tests/services/commit-service.test.js\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Foundational (T-010 ~ T-099)\n\n- [ ] [T-010] [US-1] Implement GitService.getStatus() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 获取 git 工作目录状态\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: GitStatus 对象 (clean, staged, modified, untracked, conflicts, branch)\n  - Acceptance: 返回正确的文件状态分类\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-011] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.isClean() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 检查工作目录是否干净\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: boolean\n  - Acceptance: 无变更时返回 true\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-012] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.getChangedFiles() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 获取变更文件列表\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: string[] (文件路径数组)\n  - Acceptance: 返回所有已修改/已暂存文件\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-013] [US-1][US-3] Implement GitService.commit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 执行 git commit\n  - Input: message, options (amend, allowEmpty)\n  - Output: CommitResult (success, hash, filesChanged, error)\n  - Acceptance: 成功提交返回 hash，失败返回错误信息\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-014] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.amendCommit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 修改最近一次提交\n  - Input: message\n  - Output: CommitResult\n  - Acceptance: 正确修改最近提交\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-015] [P] [US-3] Implement GitService.getLastCommit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 获取最近一次提交信息\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: CommitInfo (hash, message, author, date)\n  - Acceptance: 返回正确的最近提交信息\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-016] [P] [US-4] Implement GitService.getCommitLog() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  - Goal: 获取提交历史\n  - Input: count (optional, default 10)\n  - Output: CommitInfo[]\n  - Acceptance: 返回指定数量的提交记录\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-020] [US-2] Implement CommitService.validatePreConditions() — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 校验提交前置条件\n  - Input: ValidationOptions (skipPipelineCheck, skipTestCheck)\n  - Output: ValidationResult (valid, errors, warnings)\n  - Acceptance: 检查 pipeline 状态、测试状态、git 状态\n  - Complexity: High\n\n- [ ] [T-021] [P] [US-2] Implement pipeline status check helper — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 检查 pipeline 是否正在运行\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: { isRunning: boolean, phase: string }\n  - Acceptance: 正确判断 pipeline 状态\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-022] [P] [US-2] Implement test status check helper — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 检查测试是否通过\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: { passed: boolean, failed: number }\n  - Acceptance: 正确读取测试状态文件\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-030] [US-1][US-3] Implement CommitService.commit() main flow — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 编排完整提交流程\n  - Input: CommitParams (sessionId, userId, message, amend, force, featureId)\n  - Output: CommitResult\n  - Acceptance: 按顺序执行校验→提交→记录\n  - Complexity: High\n\n- [ ] [T-031] [P] [US-4] Implement CommitService.recordCommit() — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 记录提交到会话状态\n  - Input: sessionId, commitInfo\n  - Output: void\n  - Acceptance: 正确写入会话文件\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-032] [P] [US-4] Implement CommitService.getSessionCommits() — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 获取会话提交历史\n  - Input: sessionId\n  - Output: CommitRecord[]\n  - Acceptance: 返回当前会话的所有提交\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-040] [US-4] Extend session-store.js with commit tracking — file: src/services/session-store.js\n  - Goal: 添加 commits 字段和相关方法\n  - Input: sessionId, commitInfo\n  - Output: 更新后的 session\n  - Acceptance: 会话 JSON 包含 commits 数组\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: User Stories (T-100+)\n\n- [ ] [T-100] [US-1] Implement /commit command handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n  - Goal: 处理 /commit Telegram 命令\n  - Input: ctx (Telegram context)\n  - Output: 发送提交结果消息\n  - Acceptance: 解析参数、调用服务、格式化返回\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-101] [P] [US-1] Implement commit message builder — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n  - Goal: 构建标准提交消息格式\n  - Input: userMessage, featureId, bugfixId\n  - Output: 格式化的 commit message\n  - Acceptance: 包含 footer (feature/bugfix 关联)\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-102] [P] [US-1] Implement commit result formatter — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n  - Goal: 格式化提交结果为 Telegram 消息\n  - Input: CommitResult\n  - Output: 格式化的消息字符串\n  - Acceptance: 成功/失败消息清晰可读\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-103] [US-5] Add commit command to permission matrix — file: src/security/permission-guard.js\n  - Goal: 配置 commit 相关权限\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: 更新 COMMAND_MIN_ROLE\n  - Acceptance: commit=operator, amend/force=admin\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-104] [US-5] Implement amend confirmation flow — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n  - Goal: 处理 --amend 的确认流程\n  - Input: ctx, confirmId\n  - Output: 确认消息或执行提交\n  - Acceptance: 复用 ConfirmationManager\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-105] [US-5] Implement force confirmation flow — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n  - Goal: 处理 --force 的确认流程\n  - Input: ctx, confirmId\n  - Output: 确认消息或执行提交\n  - Acceptance: 复用 ConfirmationManager\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-110] [US-4] Implement /commits command handler — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js\n  - Goal: 处理 /commits Telegram 命令\n  - Input: ctx (Telegram context)\n  - Output: 发送提交历史列表\n  - Acceptance: 显示当前会话所有提交\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-111] [P] [US-4] Implement commits history formatter — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js\n  - Goal: 格式化提交历史为 Telegram 消息\n  - Input: CommitRecord[]\n  - Output: 格式化的列表消息\n  - Acceptance: 显示 hash、消息、时间、文件数\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-120] [US-4] Add last commit to /status output — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js\n  - Goal: 在状态查询中显示最近提交\n  - Input: 现有 status 输出\n  - Output: 追加 lastCommit 字段\n  - Acceptance: 显示最近一次提交的 hash 和消息\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-130] [US-3] Implement error message suggestions — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  - Goal: 为各类错误提供诊断建议\n  - Input: error code\n  - Output: user-friendly message + suggestion\n  - Acceptance: 每种错误都有明确建议\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Testing (T-200+)\n\n- [ ] [T-200] [P] Unit tests for GitService.getStatus() — file: tests/services/git-service.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试状态获取各种场景\n  - Input: mock git responses\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖 clean/dirty/conflict 分支\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-201] [P] Unit tests for GitService.commit() — file: tests/services/git-service.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试提交操作\n  - Input: mock git responses\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖成功/失败/空提交场景\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-202] [P] Unit tests for GitService.amendCommit() — file: tests/services/git-service.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试 amend 操作\n  - Input: mock git responses\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖成功/失败场景\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-210] [P] Unit tests for CommitService.validatePreConditions() — file: tests/services/commit-service.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试前置条件校验\n  - Input: mock status aggregator, test status\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖各校验失败场景\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-211] [P] Unit tests for CommitService.commit() — file: tests/services/commit-service.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试主提交流程\n  - Input: mock git service, session store\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖正常/异常流程\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-220] [P] Unit tests for /commit handler — file: tests/bot/commands/handlers/commit.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试命令处理逻辑\n  - Input: mock telegram context\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖参数解析、权限检查、结果格式化\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-221] [P] Unit tests for /commits handler — file: tests/bot/commands/handlers/commits.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试历史查询逻辑\n  - Input: mock session store\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 覆盖有/无提交记录场景\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-230] Integration test: commit success flow — file: tests/integration/commit-flow.test.js\n  - Goal: 端到端测试成功提交流程\n  - Input: mock git, real services\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 验证完整流程正确\n  - Complexity: High\n\n- [ ] [T-231] [P] Integration test: commit validation failure — file: tests/integration/commit-validation.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试校验失败场景\n  - Input: mock failing conditions\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 各校验错误正确返回\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-232] [P] Integration test: amend flow — file: tests/integration/commit-amend.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试 amend 流程\n  - Input: mock admin user, confirmation\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 确认流程正确执行\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n- [ ] [T-233] [P] Integration test: force flow — file: tests/integration/commit-force.test.js\n  - Goal: 测试 force 跳过校验流程\n  - Input: mock admin user, confirmation, failing conditions\n  - Output: 测试通过\n  - Acceptance: 跳过校验并成功提交\n  - Complexity: Medium\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Polish (T-900+)\n\n- [ ] [T-900] Register /commit command in bot router — file: src/bot/telegram.js\n  - Goal: 注册新命令到 Telegram bot\n  - Input: 无\n  - Output: 命令可被触发\n  - Acceptance: /commit 和 /commits 命令可用\n  - Complexity: Low\n\n- [ ] [T-901] Update help te