{"type":"user","uuid":"866016fe-c371-4ee4-8cc5-948033c308b2","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdebfd06760b7d02cd331bbc03246","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n\n**F-008: Commit Workflow Integration** 规划已完成。\n\n### 产出物\n\n| 文件 | 路径 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| spec.md | `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/spec.md` | ✅ 已创建 |\n| plan.md | `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/plan.md` | ✅ 已创建 |\n| tasks.md | `.prizmkit/specs/008-commit-workflow-integration/tasks.md` | ✅ 已创建 |\n\n### 规划摘要\n\n**功能概述:** 打通 Telegram 侧提交闭环，支持 `/commit` 触发标准提交流程，包含前置校验、权限控制、结果反馈和会话追踪。\n\n**用户故事:**\n- US-1: Telegram Commit Trigger\n- US-2: Pre-Commit Validation\n- US-3: Commit Result Feedback\n- US-4: Session Commit Tracking\n- US-5: High-Risk Commit Protection\n\n**核心组件:**\n- `GitService` - git 操作封装 (simple-git)\n- `CommitService` - 提交业务编排\n- `/commit` handler - 命令处理入口\n- `/commits` handler - 历史查询\n\n**任务统计:**\n- 总任务数: 51\n- 可并行任务: 33 [P]\n- 阶段分布: Setup(6) → Foundational(14) → User Stories(15) → Testing(12) → Polish(4)\n\n**依赖关系:**\n- F-005 (Pipeline Status) - 状态检查\n- F-006 (Safety Guard) - 权限与确认机制\n- F-007 (Test Suite) - 测试基础设施\n- simple-git (新增依赖) - git 操作封装\n\n[Agent ID: agent-5bcaaadc]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdebfd06760b7d02cd331bbc03246","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:16:48.204Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
