{"type":"user","uuid":"5d51edcc-80a1-46f6-93c5-0ee664b54c4e","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec347cd82b2a470f9018827dea2","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→---\n   2→name: prizm-dev-team-dev\n   3→description: PrizmKit-integrated module implementer (multi-instance). Follows prizmkit.implement workflow with TDD, marks tasks [x] in tasks.md, works within assigned Git worktrees. Use when implementing specific feature modules.\n   4→tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep, TaskCreate, TaskGet, TaskUpdate, TaskList, SendMessage\n   5→model: inherit\n   6→skills: prizmkit-implement, prizmkit-prizm-docs\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→你是 **Dev Agent**，PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent 软件开发协作团队的模块实现者。\n  10→\n  11→### 核心身份\n  12→\n  13→你是团队的\"建筑工人\"——严格按图纸施工，使用 PrizmKit 的 implement 工作流作为执行引擎，专注于：\n  14→- 按照 tasks.md 和 plan.md 中的接口设计逐任务实现功能模块\n  15→- 遵循 TDD 方式开发（测试先行）\n  16→- 完成后立即标记 tasks.md 中的 `[x]`\n  17→- 产出代码和单元测试\n  18→\n  19→### 项目上下文\n  20→\n  21→项目文档在 `.prizm-docs/`。实现前先读 `root.prizm` 了解规则和已知陷阱（TRAPS），修改某模块时读该模块的文档。\n  22→\n  23→### 制品路径\n  24→\n  25→| 路径 | 用途 |\n  26→|------|------|\n  27→| `.prizm-docs/` | 项目知识层 — 规则、模式、已知陷阱 |\n  28→| `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` | 功能制品 — spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md |\n  29→\n  30→### 必须做 (MUST)\n  31→\n  32→1. 按照分配的任务和 plan.md 中的接口设计实现功能模块\n  33→2. 遵循 TDD 方式：先写测试，再实现，再验证\n  34→3. 产出的代码必须通过本模块的单元测试\n  35→4. 发现接口设计歧义时，立即通过 Coordinator 上报 PM（不自行假设）\n  36→5. 遵循 `prizmkit.implement` 工作流：读取 tasks.md + plan.md + spec.md，逐任务实现\n  37→6. 每个任务完成后**立即**标记 tasks.md 中的 `[x]`（不批量标记）\n  38→7. 实现前读取 `.prizm-docs/` TRAPS 段避免已知陷阱\n  39→8. 检查点任务须验证构建通过和测试通过后才能继续下一阶段\n  40→9. 顺序任务按序执行，失败则停止；并行 `[P]` 任务可继续\n  41→10. 新建子模块时，生成对应的 `.prizm-docs/` L2 文档\n  42→\n  43→### 绝不做 (NEVER)\n  44→\n  45→- 不修改 plan.md 中的接口设计（修改需通过 PM）\n  46→- 不修改其他 Dev Agent 负责的模块代码\n  47→- 不进行集成测试（Reviewer 的职责）\n  48→- 不直接运行 git commit（由 Coordinator 通过 prizmkit.committer 统一提交）\n  49→- 不修改 `.prizmkit/specs/` 中除 `tasks.md`（标记 [x]）以外的任何文件\n  50→- 不为 bug 修复创建新的文档条目；bug 修复是现有功能的完善，应更新原始功能的文档而非在 REGISTRY.md 中创建新条目\n  51→\n  52→### 行为规则\n  53→\n  54→```\n  55→DEV-01: 实现必须严格符合 plan.md 中定义的接口设计\n  56→DEV-02: 每个公开 API/函数必须有对应的单元测试\n  57→DEV-03: 发现接口设计歧义时，不得自行假设，必须上报\n  58→DEV-04: 任务完成后必须运行全部本模块测试\n  59→DEV-05: 代码提交信息遵循 Conventional Commits 格式\n  60→DEV-06: 不得引入未在任务描述中声明的外部依赖\n  61→DEV-07: 遵循 prizmkit.implement 工作流\n  62→DEV-08: 每个任务完成后立即标记 tasks.md [x]\n  63→DEV-09: TDD：先写测试 → 再实现 → 再验证\n  64→DEV-10: 实现每个模块前必须读取 .prizm-docs/ TRAPS 段\n  65→DEV-11: 检查点任务必须验证构建通过和测试通过\n  66→DEV-12: 新建子模块时生成 L2 .prizm-docs/ 文档\n  67→```\n  68→\n  69→### 工作流程\n  70→\n  71→1. 接收任务分配\n  72→2. 读取 `.prizm-docs/root.prizm` 和相关模块文档\n  73→3. 读取 `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` 中的 `tasks.md`、`plan.md`、`spec.md`\n  74→4. 对每个分配的任务，按 tasks.md 顺序执行：\n  75→   a. 读取目标文件模块的文档（检查 TRAPS 和 DECISIONS）\n  76→   b. TDD：基于验收标准编写测试 → 实现功能代码 → 运行测试验证\n  77→   c. 在 tasks.md 中标记该任务为 `[x]`\n  78→   d. 发送 STATUS_UPDATE 给 Coordinator\n  79→5. 如遇检查点任务，验证构建通过和测试通过后才继续\n  80→6. 遇到接口设计歧义，发送 ESCALATION（不自行假设）\n  81→7. 如新建了子模块，生成对应 `.prizm-docs/` L2 文档\n  82→8. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n  83→\n  84→### 异常处理\n  85→\n  86→| 场景 | 策略 |\n  87→|------|------|\n  88→| 接口设计歧义 | 标记 BLOCKED → ESCALATION → 等待 PM 裁定 |\n  89→| 单元测试失败 | 最多重试修复 3 次 → 仍失败则 ISSUE_REPORT |\n  90→| 外部依赖不可用 | 使用 Mock → 标注说明 |\n  91→| 任务超出预估 | ESCALATION → 建议 PM 拆分任务 |\n  92→\n  93→### 通信规则\n  94→\n  95→允许 Agent 之间直接通信，但关键消息和结论必须通知 Coordinator。\n  96→- 发送 STATUS_UPDATE 汇报每个子任务完成\n  97→- 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL 标志所有任务完成\n  98→- 发送 ESCALATION 上报接口歧义或任务阻塞\n  99→- 接收 TASK_ASSIGNMENT 获取分配的工作\n 100→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:17:48.348Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"2315b39c-eff8-48d8-af27-fa6b7188a3d3","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec349b6d19a3d08c748169c5ae4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→DOC_LEVEL: L0\n   2→PROJECT_NAME: PrizmClaw\n   3→PROJECT_TYPE: telegram-bridge + web-api\n   4→ADOPTION_MODE: brownfield\n   5→PLATFORM: codebuddy\n   6→LANGUAGES: JavaScript(ESM), HTML, CSS, Python, Shell\n   7→PACKAGE_MANAGER: npm\n   8→ENTRYPOINTS: src/index.js -> src/http/server.js + src/bot/telegram.js\n   9→DOC_STATUS: initialized\n  10→ASSESSMENT: ASSESSMENT.md\n  11→MIGRATION_CANDIDATE: docs/AI_CONTEXT -> not_found\n  12→\n  13→MODULE_INDEX:\n  14→- runtime: src/** -> .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm\n  15→- web-ui: public/** -> .prizm-docs/web-ui.prizm\n  16→- pipeline: dev-pipeline/** -> .prizm-docs/pipeline.prizm\n  17→- dev-team: dev-team/** -> .prizm-docs/team.prizm\n  18→- project-config: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md -> .prizm-docs/config.prizm\n  19→\n  20→LOAD_RULES:\n  21→- ON_SESSION_START: read .prizm-docs/root.prizm\n  22→- ON_TASK: load related L1 via MODULE_INDEX\n  23→- ON_EDIT: load/create related L2 lazily\n  24→\n  25→DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:\n  26→- outdated_major: dotenv,express,zod\n  27→- npm_audit_prod: 0 vulnerabilities\n  28→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:17:48.348Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"7fd1c821-b754-4324-b493-aa00c6f54f35","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec34b52145cdcb446a76050a74f","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-008: Commit Workflow Integration\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→打通 Telegram 侧\"规划→开发→测试→提交\"的闭环提交能力：在 pipeline 通过后可触发标准提交流程，回传 commit 结果摘要，并在前置条件不满足时阻止提交。该功能不涉及部署上线，只覆盖代码提交阶段。\n   6→\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→## User Stories\n  10→\n  11→### US-1: Telegram Commit Trigger\n  12→\n  13→**As a** 开发者 **I want** 通过 `/commit` 命令触发标准提交流程 **So that** 我可以在 Telegram 中完成代码提交而无需切换到终端\n  14→\n  15→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  16→- AC-1.1: `/commit` 命令可触发提交流程\n  17→- AC-1.2: 支持 `--message=\"...\"` 参数指定提交信息\n  18→- AC-1.3: 支持 `--amend` 参数修改最近一次提交（仅 admin）\n  19→- AC-1.4: 返回 commit hash 与变更摘要\n  20→\n  21→### US-2: Pre-Commit Validation\n  22→\n  23→**As a** 系统 **I want** 提交前自动校验测试结果与 pipeline 状态 **So that** 未通过检查的代码不会被提交\n  24→\n  25→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  26→- AC-2.1: 检查 pipeline 状态，非 completed/idle 时拒绝提交\n  27→- AC-2.2: 检查测试状态文件，未通过时拒绝提交\n  28→- AC-2.3: 前置条件不满足时返回明确拒绝原因\n  29→- AC-2.4: 支持 `--force` 跳过校验（仅 admin，需二次确认）\n  30→\n  31→### US-3: Commit Result Feedback\n  32→\n  33→**As a** 开发者 **I want** 提交后收到详细的结果反馈 **So that** 我可以确认提交是否成功\n  34→\n  35→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  36→- AC-3.1: 成功时返回 commit hash（短格式）、作者、时间、变更文件数\n  37→- AC-3.2: 失败时返回明确错误原因与建议操作\n  38→- AC-3.3: 无变更时返回\"nothing to commit\"提示\n  39→- AC-3.4: 合并冲突时返回冲突文件列表\n  40→\n  41→### US-4: Session Commit Tracking\n  42→\n  43→**As a** 开发者 **I want** 提交记录与当前 feature/bugfix 关联 **So that** 我可以追溯每次提交的上下文\n  44→\n  45→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  46→- AC-4.1: 提交记录写入会话状态，关联 feature/bugfix ID\n  47→- AC-4.2: `/status` 命令显示最近一次提交信息\n  48→- AC-4.3: 支持 `/commits` 命令查看当前会话提交历史\n  49→\n  50→### US-5: High-Risk Commit Protection\n  51→\n  52→**As a** 系统管理员 **I want** 高风险提交操作需要确认 **So that** 误操作可以被阻止\n  53→\n  54→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  55→- AC-5.1: `--amend` 需要 admin 权限 + 二次确认\n  56→- AC-5.2: `--force` 跳过校验需要 admin 权限 + 二次确认\n  57→- AC-5.3: 所有提交操作写入审计日志\n  58→\n  59→---\n  60→\n  61→## Non-Functional Requirements\n  62→\n  63→### NFR-1: Performance\n  64→- 提交操作响应 < 5s（本地 git 操作）\n  65→- 状态检查 < 200ms\n  66→\n  67→### NFR-2: Reliability\n  68→- Git 操作失败不阻塞系统\n  69→- 审计日志异步写入\n  70→\n  71→### NFR-3: Security\n  72→- 复用 F-006 权限模型\n  73→- commit 列为 operator 级命令\n  74→- --amend/--force 列为 admin 级命令\n  75→\n  76→---\n  77→\n  78→## Scope Boundaries\n  79→\n  80→### In Scope\n  81→- `/commit` 命令与 handler\n  82→- Pre-commit 校验服务\n  83→- Git 操作封装服务\n  84→- 会话提交记录追踪\n  85→- `/commits` 命令\n  86→\n  87→### Out of Scope\n  88→- 部署与发布流程\n  89→- 远程仓库 push 操作\n  90→- 分支管理\n  91→- PR/MR 创建\n  92→\n  93→---\n  94→\n  95→## Dependencies\n  96→\n  97→| Dependency | Type | Status | Notes |\n  98→|------------|------|--------|-------|\n  99→| F-005 | Feature | completed | Pipeline 状态检查 |\n 100→| F-006 | Feature | completed | 权限与确认机制 |\n 101→| F-007 | Feature | completed | 测试基础设施 |\n 102→| simple-git | Library | to install | Git 操作封装 |\n 103→\n 104→---\n 105→\n 106→## Risks\n 107→\n 108→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n 109→|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n 110→| Git 操作失败 | Medium | Low | 明确错误信息，建议手动处理 |\n 111→| 工作目录脏状态 | Medium | Medium | 提交前检查，提示用户 |\n 112→| 网络问题影响 fetch | Low | Low | 仅本地操作，不依赖网络 |\n 113→\n 114→---\n 115→\n 116→## Decisions\n 117→\n 118→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 119→|----|------|----------|\n 120→| D1 | 2026-03-15 | 使用 simple-git 库封装 git 操作 |\n 121→| D2 | 2026-03-15 | commit 命令归入 operator 权限级 |\n 122→| D3 | 2026-03-15 | 不自动 push，仅本地提交 |\n 123→| D4 | 2026-03-15 | 提交记录存储于会话状态文件 |\n 124→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:17:48.349Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"d128c893-8732-45ab-9850-e3835f52c8b1","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec34d6e2b6acdb1be311395f05b","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Technical Plan\n   2→\n   3→## Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                        Telegram Bot                              │\n   8→│  /commit, /commits commands                                      │\n   9→└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n  10→                          │\n  11→┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n  12→│              Command Handler Layer                               │\n  13→│  src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js                             │\n  14→│  src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js                            │\n  15→└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n  16→                          │\n  17→┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n  18→│              Security Layer (F-006)                              │\n  19→│  PermissionGuard → ConfirmationManager → AuditLogService         │\n  20→└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n  21→                          │\n  22→┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n  23→│              Commit Service Layer                                │\n  24→│  src/services/commit-service.js                                  │\n  25→│  ├── validatePreConditions() → StatusAggregator                  │\n  26→│  ├── executeCommit() → GitService                                │\n  27→│  └── recordCommit() → SessionStore                               │\n  28→└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n  29→                          │\n  30→┌─────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────┐\n  31→│              Infrastructure Layer                                │\n  32→│  src/services/git-service.js (simple-git wrapper)                │\n  33→│  src/services/status-aggregator.js (F-005)                       │\n  34→│  src/services/session-store.js                                   │\n  35→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  36→```\n  37→\n  38→---\n  39→\n  40→## Component Design\n  41→\n  42→### C-1: GitService (`src/services/git-service.js`)\n  43→\n  44→**Purpose:** 封装所有 git 操作，提供统一 API\n  45→\n  46→**Methods:**\n  47→```javascript\n  48→interface GitService {\n  49→  // 状态检查\n  50→  getStatus(): Promise<GitStatus>\n  51→  isClean(): Promise<boolean>\n  52→  getChangedFiles(): Promise<string[]>\n  53→  \n  54→  // 提交操作\n  55→  commit(message: string, options?: CommitOptions): Promise<CommitResult>\n  56→  amendCommit(message: string): Promise<CommitResult>\n  57→  getLastCommit(): Promise<CommitInfo>\n  58→  \n  59→  // 信息获取\n  60→  getCommitLog(count?: number): Promise<CommitInfo[]>\n  61→  getShortHash(hash: string): string\n  62→}\n  63→\n  64→interface GitStatus {\n  65→  clean: boolean\n  66→  staged: string[]\n  67→  modified: string[]\n  68→  untracked: string[]\n  69→  conflicts: string[]\n  70→  ahead: number\n  71→  behind: number\n  72→  currentBranch: string\n  73→}\n  74→\n  75→interface CommitResult {\n  76→  success: boolean\n  77→  hash?: string\n  78→  shortHash?: string\n  79→  message?: string\n  80→  filesChanged?: number\n  81→  error?: string\n  82→  suggestion?: string\n  83→}\n  84→\n  85→interface CommitOptions {\n  86→  amend?: boolean\n  87→  allowEmpty?: boolean\n  88→}\n  89→```\n  90→\n  91→### C-2: CommitService (`src/services/commit-service.js`)\n  92→\n  93→**Purpose:** 提交业务逻辑编排，协调校验、执行、记录\n  94→\n  95→**Methods:**\n  96→```javascript\n  97→interface CommitService {\n  98→  // 主入口\n  99→  commit(params: CommitParams): Promise<CommitResult>\n 100→  \n 101→  // 校验\n 102→  validatePreConditions(options: ValidationOptions): Promise<ValidationResult>\n 103→  \n 104→  // 记录\n 105→  recordCommit(sessionId: string, commitInfo: CommitInfo): Promise<void>\n 106→  getSessionCommits(sessionId: string): Promise<CommitRecord[]>\n 107→}\n 108→\n 109→interface CommitParams {\n 110→  sessionId: string\n 111→  userId: string\n 112→  message?: string\n 113→  amend?: boolean\n 114→  force?: boolean\n 115→  featureId?: string\n 116→  bugfixId?: string\n 117→}\n 118→\n 119→interface ValidationOptions {\n 120→  skipPipelineCheck?: boolean\n 121→  skipTestCheck?: boolean\n 122→}\n 123→\n 124→interface ValidationResult {\n 125→  valid: boolean\n 126→  errors: ValidationError[]\n 127→  warnings: ValidationWarning[]\n 128→}\n 129→\n 130→interface ValidationError {\n 131→  code: string\n 132→  message: string\n 133→  suggestion: string\n 134→}\n 135→\n 136→interface CommitRecord {\n 137→  hash: string\n 138→  shortHash: string\n 139→  message: string\n 140→  timestamp: number\n 141→  author: string\n 142→  featureId?: string\n 143→  bugfixId?: string\n 144→  filesChanged: number\n 145→}\n 146→```\n 147→\n 148→### C-3: Commit Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js`)\n 149→\n 150→**Purpose:** Telegram 命令处理入口\n 151→\n 152→**Flow:**\n 153→1. 解析命令参数 (`--message`, `--amend`, `--force`)\n 154→2. 权限检查 (`operator` for commit, `admin` for amend/force)\n 155→3. 高风险操作确认流程 (amend/force)\n 156→4. 调用 CommitService.commit()\n 157→5. 格式化返回结果\n 158→6. 记录审计日志\n 159→\n 160→### C-4: Commits Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js`)\n 161→\n 162→**Purpose:** 查看会话提交历史\n 163→\n 164→**Flow:**\n 165→1. 获取当前会话 ID\n 166→2. 调用 CommitService.getSessionCommits()\n 167→3. 格式化历史列表返回\n 168→\n 169→---\n 170→\n 171→## Interface Design\n 172→\n 173→### I-1: Pre-Commit Validation API\n 174→\n 175→```javascript\n 176→// src/services/commit-service.js\n 177→\n 178→const VALIDATION_ERRORS = {\n 179→  PIPELINE_RUNNING: {\n 180→    code: 'PIPELINE_RUNNING',\n 181→    message: 'Pipeline 正在运行中',\n 182→    suggestion: '请等待 pipeline 完成或使用 /stop 停止'\n 183→  },\n 184→  TEST_FAILED: {\n 185→    code: 'TEST_FAILED',\n 186→    message: '测试未通过',\n 187→    suggestion: '请检查测试结果或使用 --force 跳过（仅 admin）'\n 188→  },\n 189→  NOTHING_TO_COMMIT: {\n 190→    code: 'NOTHING_TO_COMMIT',\n 191→    message: '没有待提交的变更',\n 192→    suggestion: '请先进行代码修改'\n 193→  },\n 194→  MERGE_CONFLICT: {\n 195→    code: 'MERGE_CONFLICT',\n 196→    message: '存在合并冲突',\n 197→    suggestion: '请先解决以下冲突文件：{files}'\n 198→  }\n 199→};\n 200→\n 201→async function validatePreConditions(options) {\n 202→  const errors = [];\n 203→  const warnings = [];\n 204→  \n 205→  // 1. Check pipeline status (via status-aggregator)\n 206→  const pipelineStatus = await statusAggregator.aggregateStatus();\n 207→  if (pipelineStatus.phase === 'running' && !options.skipPipelineCheck) {\n 208→    errors.push(VALIDATION_ERRORS.PIPELINE_RUNNING);\n 209→  }\n 210→  \n 211→  // 2. Check test status (from state file)\n 212→  const testStatus = await getTestStatus();\n 213→  if (testStatus.failed > 0 && !options.skipTestCheck) {\n 214→    errors.push(VALIDATION_ERRORS.TEST_FAILED);\n 215→  }\n 216→  \n 217→  // 3. Check git status\n 218→  const gitStatus = await gitService.getStatus();\n 219→  if (gitStatus.clean) {\n 220→    errors.push(VALIDATION_ERRORS.NOTHING_TO_COMMIT);\n 221→  }\n 222→  if (gitStatus.conflicts.length > 0) {\n 223→    errors.push({\n 224→      ...VALIDATION_ERRORS.MERGE_CONFLICT,\n 225→      files: gitStatus.conflicts\n 226→    });\n 227→  }\n 228→  \n 229→  return {\n 230→    valid: errors.length === 0,\n 231→    errors,\n 232→    warnings,\n 233→    gitStatus\n 234→  };\n 235→}\n 236→```\n 237→\n 238→### I-2: Commit Execution API\n 239→\n 240→```javascript\n 241→// src/services/git-service.js\n 242→\n 243→async function commit(message, options = {}) {\n 244→  try {\n 245→    // Build commit message with footer\n 246→    const fullMessage = buildCommitMessage(message, options);\n 247→    \n 248→    // Execute git commit\n 249→    const result = await git.commit(fullMessage);\n 250→    \n 251→    if (!result.commit) {\n 252→      return {\n 253→        success: false,\n 254→        error: '提交失败',\n 255→        suggestion: '请检查 git 状态'\n 256→      };\n 257→    }\n 258→    \n 259→    return {\n 260→      success: true,\n 261→      hash: result.commit,\n 262→      shortHash: result.commit.substring(0, 7),\n 263→      message: fullMessage,\n 264→      filesChanged: result.summary.changes\n 265→    };\n 266→  } catch (error) {\n 267→    return {\n 268→      success: false,\n 269→      error: error.message,\n 270→      suggestion: getSuggestion(error)\n 271→    };\n 272→  }\n 273→}\n 274→```\n 275→\n 276→### I-3: Session Commit Tracking\n 277→\n 278→```javascript\n 279→// 扩展 src/services/session-store.js\n 280→\n 281→// Session state structure (JSON file)\n 282→{\n 283→  \"sessionId\": \"abc123\",\n 284→  \"featureId\": \"F-008\",\n 285→  \"createdAt\": 1710489600000,\n 286→  \"commits\": [\n 287→    {\n 288→      \"hash\": \"a1b2c3d4e5f6...\",\n 289→      \"shortHash\": \"a1b2c3d\",\n 290→      \"message\": \"feat: add commit workflow\",\n 291→      \"timestamp\": 1710489700000,\n 292→      \"author\": \"user\",\n 293→      \"filesChanged\": 5\n 294→    }\n 295→  ]\n 296→}\n 297→\n 298→// API\n 299→async function addCommitToSession(sessionId, commitInfo) {\n 300→  const session = await loadSession(sessionId);\n 301→  session.commits = session.commits || [];\n 302→  session.commits.push({\n 303→    ...commitInfo,\n 304→    timestamp: Date.now()\n 305→  });\n 306→  await saveSession(session);\n 307→}\n 308→\n 309→async function getSessionCommits(sessionId) {\n 310→  const session = await loadSession(sessionId);\n 311→  return session.commits || [];\n 312→}\n 313→```\n 314→\n 315→---\n 316→\n 317→## Data Model\n 318→\n 319→### D-1: Session State (Extended)\n 320→\n 321→```javascript\n 322→// File: data/sessions/{sessionId}.json\n 323→{\n 324→  \"sessionId\": \"string\",\n 325→  \"featureId\": \"string | null\",\n 326→  \"bugfixId\": \"string | null\",\n 327→  \"createdAt\": \"number (timestamp)\",\n 328→  \"updatedAt\": \"number (timestamp)\",\n 329→  \"commits\": [\n 330→    {\n 331→      \"hash\": \"string (full hash)\",\n 332→      \"shortHash\": \"string (7 chars)\",\n 333→      \"message\": \"string\",\n 334→      \"timestamp\": \"number\",\n 335→      \"author\": \"string\",\n 336→      \"filesChanged\": \"number\"\n 337→    }\n 338→  ]\n 339→}\n 340→```\n 341→\n 342→### D-2: Test Status (Existing)\n 343→\n 344→```javascript\n 345→// File: dev-pipeline/state/test-status.json (由 F-007 创建)\n 346→{\n 347→  \"lastRun\": \"number (timestamp)\",\n 348→  \"passed\": \"number\",\n 349→  \"failed\": \"number\",\n 350→  \"skipped\": \"number\",\n 351→  \"duration\": \"number (ms)\"\n 352→}\n 353→```\n 354→\n 355→---\n 356→\n 357→## Command Permission Matrix\n 358→\n 359→| Command | Min Role | Confirmation | Notes |\n 360→|---------|----------|--------------|-------|\n 361→| `/commit` | operator | No | 标准提交 |\n 362→| `/commit --amend` | admin | Yes | 修改最近提交 |\n 363→| `/commit --force` | admin | Yes | 跳过校验 |\n 364→| `/commits` | viewer | No | 查看历史 |\n 365→\n 366→---\n 367→\n 368→## Testing Strategy\n 369→\n 370→### Unit Tests\n 371→\n 372→| Module | Test File | Coverage Target |\n 373→|--------|-----------|-----------------|\n 374→| GitService | tests/services/git-service.test.js | 90% |\n 375→| CommitService | tests/services/commit-service.test.js | 90% |\n 376→| commit handler | tests/bot/commands/handlers/commit.test.js | 85% |\n 377→| commits handler | tests/bot/commands/handlers/commits.test.js | 85% |\n 378→\n 379→### Integration Tests\n 380→\n 381→| Scenario | Test File | Priority |\n 382→|----------|-----------|----------|\n 383→| commit → success flow | tests/integration/commit-flow.test.js | High |\n 384→| commit → validation failure | tests/integration/commit-validation.test.js | High |\n 385→| commit → amend flow | tests/integration/commit-amend.test.js | Medium |\n 386→| commit → force flow | tests/integration/commit-force.test.js | Medium |\n 387→\n 388→### Mock Strategy\n 389→\n 390→- GitService: 使用 mock git responses，不执行真实 git 命令\n 391→- StatusAggregator: 复用 F-005 mock 策略\n 392→- SessionStore: 使用临时目录\n 393→\n 394→---\n 395→\n 396→## File Structure\n 397→\n 398→```\n 399→src/\n 400→├── services/\n 401→│   ├── git-service.js          # NEW - git 操作封装\n 402→│   ├── commit-service.js       # NEW - 提交业务逻辑\n 403→│   └── session-store.js        # EXTEND - 添加 commit tracking\n 404→├── bot/\n 405→│   └── commands/\n 406→│       └── handlers/\n 407→│           ├── commit.js       # NEW - /commit 命令\n 408→│           └── commits.js      # NEW - /commits 命令\n 409→tests/\n 410→├── services/\n 411→│   ├── git-service.test.js     # NEW\n 412→│   └── commit-service.test.js  # NEW\n 413→├── bot/\n 414→│   └── commands/\n 415→│       └── handlers/\n 416→│           ├── commit.test.js  # NEW\n 417→│           └── commits.test.js # NEW\n 418→└── integration/\n 419→    ├── commit-flow.test.js     # NEW\n 420→    └── commit-validation.test.js # NEW\n 421→```\n 422→\n 423→---\n 424→\n 425→## User Story Mapping\n 426→\n 427→| User Story | Components | Key Files |\n 428→|------------|------------|-----------|\n 429→| US-1: Telegram Commit Trigger | C-3, C-2 | commit.js, commit-service.js |\n 430→| US-2: Pre-Commit Validation | C-2 | commit-service.js |\n 431→| US-3: Commit Result Feedback | C-1, C-3 | git-service.js, commit.js |\n 432→| US-4: Session Commit Tracking | C-2, C-4 | commit-service.js, session-store.js, commits.js |\n 433→| US-5: High-Risk Commit Protection | Security Layer | commit.js, permission-guard.js |\n 434→\n 435→---\n 436→\n 437→## Risk Mitigation\n 438→\n 439→| Risk | Mitigation Strategy |\n 440→|------|---------------------|\n 441→| Git 操作失败 | GitService 返回详细错误 + 建议操作 |\n 442→| 工作目录脏状态 | 提交前 isClean() 检查 |\n 443→| 测试状态文件缺失 | 容错处理，视为\"未运行测试\"警告 |\n 444→| 会话文件损坏 | try-catch + 空数组回退 |\n 445→\n 446→---\n 447→\n 448→## Dependencies Check\n 449→\n 450→| Dependency | Required By | Install Command |\n 451→|------------|-------------|-----------------|\n 452→| simple-git | GitService | `npm install simple-git` |\n 453→\n 454→---\n 455→\n 456→## Decisions\n 457→\n 458→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 459→|----|------|----------|\n 460→| D1 | 2026-03-15 | 使用 simple-git 库封装 git 操作，避免 shell 注入风险 |\n 461→| D2 | 2026-03-15 | Pre-commit 校验包含 pipeline 状态和测试状态双重检查 |\n 462→| D3 | 2026-03-15 | 提交记录存储于会话状态文件，不新建独立存储 |\n 463→| D4 | 2026-03-15 | 复用 F-006 确认机制处理 amend/force 高风险操作 |\n 464→| D5 | 2026-03-15 | GitService 设计为可 mock，便于单元测试 |\n 465→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:17:48.350Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"b66d3f9c-d1f7-4448-bb55-89e3d633579c","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec34f724276fe036458d5da5bbf","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Task Breakdown\n   2→\n   3→## Phase 1: Setup (T-001 ~ T-009)\n   4→\n   5→- [ ] [T-001] [P] Install simple-git dependency — file: package.json\n   6→- [ ] [T-002] [P] Create git-service.js module skeleton — file: src/services/git-service.js\n   7→- [ ] [T-003] [P] Create commit-service.js module skeleton — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n   8→- [ ] [T-004] [P] Create commit handler skeleton — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n   9→- [ ] [P] Create commits handler skeleton — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js\n  10→- [ ] [T-006] [P] Create test file skeletons — file: tests/services/git-service.test.js, tests/services/commit-service.test.js\n  11→\n  12→---\n  13→\n  14→## Phase 2: Foundational (T-010 ~ T-099)\n  15→\n  16→- [ ] [T-010] [US-1] Implement GitService.getStatus() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  17→  - Goal: 获取 git 工作目录状态\n  18→  - Input: 无\n  19→  - Output: GitStatus 对象 (clean, staged, modified, untracked, conflicts, branch)\n  20→  - Acceptance: 返回正确的文件状态分类\n  21→  - Complexity: Medium\n  22→\n  23→- [ ] [T-011] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.isClean() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  24→  - Goal: 检查工作目录是否干净\n  25→  - Input: 无\n  26→  - Output: boolean\n  27→  - Acceptance: 无变更时返回 true\n  28→  - Complexity: Low\n  29→\n  30→- [ ] [T-012] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.getChangedFiles() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  31→  - Goal: 获取变更文件列表\n  32→  - Input: 无\n  33→  - Output: string[] (文件路径数组)\n  34→  - Acceptance: 返回所有已修改/已暂存文件\n  35→  - Complexity: Low\n  36→\n  37→- [ ] [T-013] [US-1][US-3] Implement GitService.commit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  38→  - Goal: 执行 git commit\n  39→  - Input: message, options (amend, al