{"type":"user","uuid":"7e589359-dc2a-4317-953d-0861ef25d6ed","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec881f89d96290c6d60091321a9","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Task Breakdown\n   2→\n   3→## Phase 1: Setup (T-001 ~ T-009)\n   4→\n   5→- [x] [T-001] [P] Install simple-git dependency — file: package.json\n   6→- [x] [T-002] [P] Create git-service.js module skeleton — file: src/services/git-service.js\n   7→- [x] [T-003] [P] Create commit-service.js module skeleton — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n   8→- [x] [T-004] [P] Create commit handler skeleton — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js\n   9→- [x] [T-005] [P] Create commits handler skeleton — file: src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js\n  10→- [x] [T-006] [P] Create test file skeletons — file: tests/services/git-service.test.js, tests/services/commit-service.test.js\n  11→\n  12→---\n  13→\n  14→## Phase 2: Foundational (T-010 ~ T-099)\n  15→\n  16→- [ ] [T-010] [US-1] Implement GitService.getStatus() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  17→  - Goal: 获取 git 工作目录状态\n  18→  - Input: 无\n  19→  - Output: GitStatus 对象 (clean, staged, modified, untracked, conflicts, branch)\n  20→  - Acceptance: 返回正确的文件状态分类\n  21→  - Complexity: Medium\n  22→\n  23→- [ ] [T-011] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.isClean() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  24→  - Goal: 检查工作目录是否干净\n  25→  - Input: 无\n  26→  - Output: boolean\n  27→  - Acceptance: 无变更时返回 true\n  28→  - Complexity: Low\n  29→\n  30→- [ ] [T-012] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.getChangedFiles() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  31→  - Goal: 获取变更文件列表\n  32→  - Input: 无\n  33→  - Output: string[] (文件路径数组)\n  34→  - Acceptance: 返回所有已修改/已暂存文件\n  35→  - Complexity: Low\n  36→\n  37→- [ ] [T-013] [US-1][US-3] Implement GitService.commit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  38→  - Goal: 执行 git commit\n  39→  - Input: message, options (amend, allowEmpty)\n  40→  - Output: CommitResult (success, hash, filesChanged, error)\n  41→  - Acceptance: 成功提交返回 hash，失败返回错误信息\n  42→  - Complexity: Medium\n  43→\n  44→- [ ] [T-014] [P] [US-1] Implement GitService.amendCommit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  45→  - Goal: 修改最近一次提交\n  46→  - Input: message\n  47→  - Output: CommitResult\n  48→  - Acceptance: 正确修改最近提交\n  49→  - Complexity: Medium\n  50→\n  51→- [ ] [T-015] [P] [US-3] Implement GitService.getLastCommit() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  52→  - Goal: 获取最近一次提交信息\n  53→  - Input: 无\n  54→  - Output: CommitInfo (hash, message, author, date)\n  55→  - Acceptance: 返回正确的最近提交信息\n  56→  - Complexity: Low\n  57→\n  58→- [ ] [T-016] [P] [US-4] Implement GitService.getCommitLog() — file: src/services/git-service.js\n  59→  - Goal: 获取提交历史\n  60→  - Input: count (optional, default 10)\n  61→  - Output: CommitInfo[]\n  62→  - Acceptance: 返回指定数量的提交记录\n  63→  - Complexity: Low\n  64→\n  65→- [ ] [T-020] [US-2] Implement CommitService.validatePreConditions() — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  66→  - Goal: 校验提交前置条件\n  67→  - Input: ValidationOptions (skipPipelineCheck, skipTestCheck)\n  68→  - Output: ValidationResult (valid, errors, warnings)\n  69→  - Acceptance: 检查 pipeline 状态、测试状态、git 状态（含冲突检测）\n  70→  - Complexity: High\n  71→\n  72→- [ ] [T-021] [P] [US-2] Implement pipeline status check helper — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  73→  - Goal: 检查 pipeline 是否正在运行\n  74→  - Input: 无\n  75→  - Output: { isRunning: boolean, phase: string }\n  76→  - Acceptance: 正确判断 pipeline 状态\n  77→  - Complexity: Low\n  78→\n  79→- [ ] [T-022] [P] [US-2] Implement test status check helper — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  80→  - Goal: 检查测试是否通过\n  81→  - Input: 无\n  82→  - Output: { passed: boolean, failed: number }\n  83→  - Acceptance: 正确读取测试状态文件\n  84→  - Complexity: Low\n  85→\n  86→- [ ] [T-030] [US-1][US-3] Implement CommitService.commit() main flow — file: src/services/commit-service.js\n  8