{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312053108058cd77b68ba48c2","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"id":"20260312053108058cd77b68ba48c2","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Let me provide a summary of the F-008 implementation:\n\n## F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Implementation Summary\n\n### Completed Components\n\n**Phase 1: Setup ✅**\n- Installed `simple-git` dependency\n- Created module skeletons for git-service, commit-service, commit/commits handlers\n\n**Phase 2: Foundational ✅**\n- **GitService** (`src/services/git-service.js`):\n  - `getStatus()` - Returns git working directory status\n  - `isClean()` - Checks if working directory is clean\n  - `getChangedFiles()` - Returns list of changed files\n  - `commit()` - Executes git commit with validation\n  - `amendCommit()` - Amends last commit\n  - `getLastCommit()` - Gets last commit info\n  - `getCommitLog()` - Gets commit history\n\n- **CommitService** (`src/services/commit-service.js`):\n  - `validatePreConditions()` - Validates pipeline/test/git status\n  - `commit()` - Main commit flow with validation → execution → recording\n  - `recordCommit()` / `getSessionCommits()` - Session commit tracking\n  - `checkPipelineStatus()` / `checkTestStatus()` - Validation helpers\n  - **Audit logging integrated (AC-5.3)** ✅\n\n- **SessionStore Extended** (`src/services/session-store.js`):\n  - `addCommit()` / `getCommits()` / `getLastCommit()` - Commit tracking\n\n**Phase 3: User Stories ✅**\n- **commit handler** (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js`):\n  - `/commit [--message=\"...\"] [--amend] [--force]`\n  - Permission checks (operator for commit, admin for amend/force)\n  - Confirmation flow for high-risk operations\n  - Audit logging for all operations\n\n- **commits handler** (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js`):\n  - `/commits [--count=N]` - View session commit history\n\n- **Permission Matrix Updated** (`src/security/permission-guard.js`):\n  - `commit` = operator\n  - `commit-amend` / `commit-force` = admin\n\n**Phase 4: Testing ✅**\n- 18 GitService tests passing\n- 24 CommitService tests passing\n- 12 commit handler tests passing\n- 8 commits handler tests passing\n\n**Phase 5: Polish ✅**\n- Commands registered in bot router\n- Help system auto-includes commands (dynamic)\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm` updated\n- `REGISTRY.md` updated with F-008 entry\n\n### Key Decisions Applied\n- **D1**: Used simple-git library (avoids shell injection)\n- **D2**: Dual pre-commit validation (pipeline + test status)\n- **D3**: Commits stored in session state file\n- **D4**: Reused F-006 ConfirmationManager for amend/force\n- **D5**: GitService designed for mockability\n\n### AC-5.3 Audit Logging ✅\nAll commit operations are logged via `logAuditEntry()`:\n- Success/failure/denied results\n- User ID, role, action, params\n- Session ID for traceability"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":153117,"output_tokens":716,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:31:23.604Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"8da7e390-b3fd-4dc0-8552-ecad302e2d41","session_id":"45bd4fe9-d12f-4930-90bb-1615d208ca29","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Let me provide a summary of the F-008 implementation:\n\n## F-008: Commit Workflow Integration - Implementation Summary\n\n### Completed Components\n\n**Phase 1: Setup ✅**\n- Installed `simple-git` dependency\n- Created module skeletons for git-service, commit-service, commit/commits handlers\n\n**Phase 2: Foundational ✅**\n- **GitService** (`src/services/git-service.js`):\n  - `getStatus()` - Returns git working directory status\n  - `isClean()` - Checks if working directory is clean\n  - `getChangedFiles()` - Returns list of changed files\n  - `commit()` - Executes git commit with validation\n  - `amendCommit()` - Amends last commit\n  - `getLastCommit()` - Gets last commit info\n  - `getCommitLog()` - Gets commit history\n\n- **CommitService** (`src/services/commit-service.js`):\n  - `validatePreConditions()` - Validates pipeline/test/git status\n  - `commit()` - Main commit flow with validation → execution → recording\n  - `recordCommit()` / `getSessionCommits()` - Session commit tracking\n  - `checkPipelineStatus()` / `checkTestStatus()` - Validation helpers\n  - **Audit logging integrated (AC-5.3)** ✅\n\n- **SessionStore Extended** (`src/services/session-store.js`):\n  - `addCommit()` / `getCommits()` / `getLastCommit()` - Commit tracking\n\n**Phase 3: User Stories ✅**\n- **commit handler** (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js`):\n  - `/commit [--message=\"...\"] [--amend] [--force]`\n  - Permission checks (operator for commit, admin for amend/force)\n  - Confirmation flow for high-risk operations\n  - Audit logging for all operations\n\n- **commits handler** (`src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js`):\n  - `/commits [--count=N]` - View session commit history\n\n- **Permission Matrix Updated** (`src/security/permission-guard.js`):\n  - `commit` = operator\n  - `commit-amend` / `commit-force` = admin\n\n**Phase 4: Testing ✅**\n- 18 GitService tests passing\n- 24 CommitService tests passing\n- 12 commit handler tests passing\n- 8 commits handler tests passing\n\n**Phase 5: Polish ✅**\n- Commands registered in bot router\n- Help system auto-includes commands (dynamic)\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm` updated\n- `REGISTRY.md` updated with F-008 entry\n\n### Key Decisions Applied\n- **D1**: Used simple-git library (avoids shell injection)\n- **D2**: Dual pre-commit validation (pipeline + test status)\n- **D3**: Commits stored in session state file\n- **D4**: Reused F-006 ConfirmationManager for amend/force\n- **D5**: GitService designed for mockability\n\n### AC-5.3 Audit Logging ✅\nAll commit operations are logged via `logAuditEntry()`:\n- Success/failure/denied results\n- User ID, role, action, params\n- Session ID for traceability\n\n[Agent ID: agent-de7725d7]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdec32d7c15d0f91483a9f4d163da","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:31:23.614Z","_requestId":"831488a1f0e5461b9b01219ae792e61e"}
